{"article_id":"wZf5f9tkb8zVFFJr","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The White House is fighting to regain control of the confirmation of Supreme Court pick Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"but a controversy is widening over its role in an FBI investigation into allegations against the nominee of sexual assault and misconduct .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"New signs emerged Sunday","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that the administration is taking steps","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"to make sure","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"the probe is narrow and focused","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"-- as Republicans seek to forestall further delays to the confirmation process or another erosion of the judge 's position .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"So","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"while President Donald Trump may have been forced to reopen an FBI background check on Kavanaugh ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"it is clear he is determined to get the process back on track in a strategy","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"already inflaming partisan discord over the nomination .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"A swift investigation by the FBI","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"-- should it produce no new information about Kavanaugh 's past","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that hurts his chances --","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"could permit Republicans to fire up the machinery of the Senate","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"and potentially call procedural votes","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"to advance the nomination by the end of the week .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Such a timetable would keep alive the effort","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"to present GOP base voters with a generational deliverable and a solid conservative majority on the Supreme Court","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that could juice turnout for midterm elections in November","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"that are looking favorable for Democrats .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"But the extent","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"to which the White House is controlling the process","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"is likely to stoke fresh turmoil around a nomination","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"that is already certain to trigger long-term political reverberations .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"The investigation is the result of a dramatic day in Washington on Friday","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"that began with quick movement toward Kavanaugh 's confirmation","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"and ended with a pause in the process","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"while the FBI steps in .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Following the agreement for the FBI to investigate Kavanaugh ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"the focus has moved to how the probe will be handled , its ultimate findings , and whether it will put to rest fears about a lack of due diligence over the nominee for the nation 's highest court .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Trump said Saturday","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that the FBI would have `` free rein ''","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"to investigate whatever it wanted in the probe ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"saying ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"`` They have free rein","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to do whatever they have to do . ''","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"But potential inconsistencies emerged Sunday between public statements by administration officials","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that appeared to finesse Trump 's assertion","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"and what some sources are saying privately about the probe .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Trump 's counselor Kellyanne Conway told CNN 's Jake Tapper on `` State of the Union ''","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that the reopened FBI checks into Kavanaugh would be `` limited in scope ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"it 's meant to last one week ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"and ... it 's not meant to be a fishing expedition . ''","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"But she also insisted","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"that Trump respects the independence of the FBI","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"and believes","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"it should look into `` anything","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"that is credible within that limited scope . ''","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"White House spokeswoman Sarah Sanders said on `` Fox News Sunday , '' meanwhile ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"that `` the White House is not micromanaging this process . ''","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"But she also warned","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"that `` Senate Republicans are going to lay out and dictate those terms ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"and we look forward to this wrapping up","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"so we can see","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"what was seen in the last six investigations","depth":15},{"id":57,"text":"that Judge Kavanaugh has been a part of . ''","depth":15},{"id":58,"text":"A source with knowledge of the investigation told CNN","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"that the FBI will interview a handful of people","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"and only take direction from the White House , not the Senate .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"A source","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"briefed on the matter","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"the White House sent the limited parameters of the investigation to the FBI","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"based on a Senate request .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"Two sources with knowledge of the situation told CNN , however ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"that Senate Republicans were working with White House counsel Don McGahn ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"who was `` trying to make it as narrow","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"as possible . ''","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"Indications","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"that the White House was intimately involved in the process","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"could risk tainting its eventual conclusions","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"or leave the impression","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"that the probe is using the prestige of the FBI","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"but is only a cursory effort","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"designed to restore Kavanaugh 's momentum as quickly as possible .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Trump was quick to try to scotch suggestions","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that the White House was taking an inappropriate interest in the investigation","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"-- doing so in a way","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"that hinted at how the storyline could explode in the days to come .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"`` Wow !","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"Just starting to hear the Democrats ,","depth":16},{"id":83,"text":"who are only thinking Obstruct and Delay ,","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"are starting to put out the word","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"that the 'time ' and 'scope ' of FBI","depth":16},{"id":86,"text":"looking into Judge Kavanaugh and witnesses","depth":16},{"id":87,"text":"is not enough .","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"Hello !","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"For them , it will never be enough -","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"stay tuned","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"and watch ! ''","depth":16},{"id":92,"text":"the President tweeted .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"The investigation only happened at all","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"because Arizona Sen. Jeff Flake blinked last week","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"and made his vote","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"to confirm Kavanaugh contingent on further inquiries into the allegations .","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"Signs","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that the White House is more closely involved","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"in setting the terms of the new background check on Kavanaugh","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"than might have been initially clear","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"sparked disquiet from Democrats .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"`` Based on some of the reports","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"we 've seen this weekend ,","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"I 'm very concerned about this","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"because the White House should not be allowed to micromanage an FBI investigation , ''","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"Democratic Sen. Amy Klobuchar of Minnesota ,","depth":16},{"id":107,"text":"who sits on the Senate Judiciary Committee ,","depth":16},{"id":108,"text":"said on CNN 's `` State of the Union . '' `` While the White House decides who to nominate ,","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"and then that person is submitted to a background check ,","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"I have never heard that the White House , either under this president or other presidents , is saying ,","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"'well , you ca n't interview this person ,","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"you ca n't look at this time period ,","depth":16},{"id":113,"text":"you can only look at these people from one side of the street","depth":17},{"id":114,"text":"from when they were growing up , ' ''","depth":17},{"id":115,"text":"Klobuchar said .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"Asked on ABC 's `` This Week ''","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"whether she thought","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"the FBI investigation would be credible ,","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"Hawaii Democratic Sen. Mazie Hirono said ,","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"`` That 's going to be the big outstanding question . ''","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"`` I would think","depth":15},{"id":122,"text":"that Jeff Flake and the other senators","depth":18},{"id":123,"text":"who are going for this investigation","depth":18},{"id":124,"text":"will call for --","depth":17},{"id":125,"text":"there 's time ,","depth":17},{"id":126,"text":"you know , ''","depth":17},{"id":127,"text":"said Hirono ,","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"who is also a Judiciary Committee member .","depth":15},{"id":129,"text":"`` The thing is that every Senate vote matters","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"and there is ... time","depth":17},{"id":131,"text":"to get to the bottom of it ,","depth":17},{"id":132,"text":"even if it 's seven days . `","depth":16},{"id":133,"text":"` That 's bad enough , ''","depth":15},{"id":134,"text":"Hirono continued .","depth":15},{"id":135,"text":"`` But then to limit the FBI as to the scope and who they 're going to question , that , that really --","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"I wanted to use the word farce --","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"but that 's not the kind of investigation","depth":15},{"id":138,"text":"that all of us are expecting the FBI to conduct . ''","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"The latest White House gambit will also , once again , drag the FBI into the heat of the political battle in Washington","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"-- an unfortunate pattern","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"that has repeated itself over the last few years","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"including with the Clinton email controversy , the Russia investigation and Trump 's constant pressure on the bureau .","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"Initially ,","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"it appears ,","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"the bureau will talk to people","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"who could shed light on Christine Blasey Ford 's allegation","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"that a drunken Kavanaugh sexually assaulted her at a house party","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"when they were teenagers .","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"This is expected to include Mark Judge ,","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"whom","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"Ford alleges","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"was in the room at the time ,","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"and two other people","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"Ford said","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"were at the party ,","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"Patrick J. Smyth and Leland Keyser ,","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"sources familiar with the matter tell CNN .","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"Judge has already said","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"that he had no memory of any alleged incident","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"involving Ford and Kavanaugh ,","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"and Smyth and Keyser have said","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"they do n't remember the party .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"However , Keyser , a friend of Ford 's , does not refute the allegation","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"and has said","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"she believes the account ,","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"her lawyer said in a letter to the Senate Judiciary Committee .","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"But Ford and Kavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"-- who gave testimony under oath to the committee on Thursday --","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"were not on the initial list of names","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"given by Senate Republicans to the White House ,","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"according to two sources familiar with the matter .","depth":7},{"id":172,"text":"Questioning Judge could go some way","depth":7},{"id":173,"text":"to easing concerns among several Republicans about the questions","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"surrounding the Ford allegations .","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"Unless he changes his story , however ,","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"it seems unlikely that the FBI investigations produce new actionable evidence","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"that could potentially disqualify Kavanaugh ,","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"especially since the alleged incident took place 36 years ago .","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"That could play into an argument","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"Republicans have used","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"to bolster Kavanagh 's confirmation hopes :","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"that he should not be blocked from the Court","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"based on allegations","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"that can not be corroborated","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"and were not prosecuted at the time .","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"Indeed , Kavanaugh 's supporters could find reason for optimism in an independent assessment of Ford 's allegation","depth":6},{"id":187,"text":"that the outside counsel at Thursday 's GOP-led Judiciary Committee hearing sent to the Republican members of the committee Sunday night .","depth":6},{"id":188,"text":"Rachel MItchell , the sex crimes prosecutor","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"who was tasked with questioning Ford on her allegation of sexual assault ,","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"a `` reasonable prosecutor '' would not bring a case against Kavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"based on Ford 's allegation","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"given the evidence","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"presented to the committee .","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"Mitchell cited inconsistencies in Ford 's statements to the committee , as well as to The Washington Post and her therapist ,","depth":8},{"id":196,"text":"and noted the lack of corroboration of her account ,","depth":9},{"id":197,"text":"including recalling details","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"that could back her story .","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"`` In the legal context , here is my bottom line :","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"A 'he said ,","depth":13},{"id":201,"text":"she said","depth":13},{"id":202,"text":"' case is incredibly difficult to prove , ''","depth":12},{"id":203,"text":"Mitchell wrote .","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"`` But this case is even weaker than that .","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"Dr. Ford identified other witnesses to the event ,","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"and those witnesses either refuted her allegations","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"or failed to corroborate them .","depth":11},{"id":208,"text":"For the reasons","depth":13},{"id":209,"text":"discussed below ,","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"I do not think","depth":12},{"id":211,"text":"that a reasonable prosecutor would bring this case","depth":12},{"id":212,"text":"based on the evidence before the Committee .","depth":12},{"id":213,"text":"Nor do I believe","depth":11},{"id":214,"text":"that this evidence is sufficient","depth":12},{"id":215,"text":"to satisfy the preponderance-of-the-evidence standard . ''","depth":12},{"id":216,"text":"Still , Democrats have argued , especially in the light of the changed politics of the # MeToo era ,","depth":6},{"id":217,"text":"that anyone","depth":9},{"id":218,"text":"elevated to the Supreme Court","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"should be above suspicion or moral reproach ,","depth":8},{"id":220,"text":"and that the allegations should be given credence","depth":8},{"id":221,"text":"even if they are not prosecuted .","depth":8},{"id":222,"text":"But the probe could potentially give Republican senators like Flake , Maine 's Susan Collins and Alaska 's Lisa Murkowski ,","depth":7},{"id":223,"text":"who were put on the spot by Ford 's emotional testimony on Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":224,"text":"more cover","depth":7},{"id":225,"text":"to vote for Kavanaugh .","depth":7},{"id":226,"text":"A source familiar with the situation told CNN 's Ariane De Vogue","depth":6},{"id":227,"text":"that the FBI had spoken on Sunday to Deborah Ramirez , another woman","depth":7},{"id":228,"text":"who came forward with allegations against Kavanaugh from his time at Yale University ,","depth":8},{"id":229,"text":"which the judge has also denied .","depth":8},{"id":230,"text":"But there is so far no indication","depth":9},{"id":231,"text":"that the FBI has or will talk with Julie Swetnick ,","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"whose attorney , Michael Avenatti , also represents Stormy Daniels , the adult film star","depth":11},{"id":233,"text":"who alleges","depth":12},{"id":234,"text":"she had an affair with Trump .","depth":12},{"id":235,"text":"Trump has denied that allegation .","depth":8},{"id":236,"text":"Swetnick has also made allegations against a young Kavanaugh ,","depth":9},{"id":237,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":238,"text":"he was present at a party","depth":13},{"id":239,"text":"in which she was raped ,","depth":13},{"id":240,"text":"and that both he and Judge would consistently engage in excessive drinking .","depth":12},{"id":241,"text":"She did not identify either Kavanaugh nor Judge as her attackers .","depth":10},{"id":242,"text":"But the President slammed Avenatti as a `` low life '' and a `` third rate lawyer ''","depth":9},{"id":243,"text":"who makes false accusations .","depth":9},{"id":244,"text":"So the chances","depth":8},{"id":245,"text":"that the White House ,","depth":9},{"id":246,"text":"if it is controlling the scope of the FBI investigation into Kavanaugh ,","depth":10},{"id":247,"text":"offers any opening to Avenatti","depth":10},{"id":248,"text":"appear slim .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":497,"left":0,"right":496,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":496,"left":390,"right":495,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":390,"left":273,"right":389,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":259,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":255,"right":258,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":250,"right":254,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":254,"left":3,"right":253,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":253,"left":252,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":252,"left":4,"right":251,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":258,"left":256,"right":257,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":256,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":264,"right":271,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":261,"right":263,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":261,"left":12,"right":260,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":15,"right":262,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":262,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":267,"right":270,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":267,"left":18,"right":266,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":19,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":265,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":268,"right":269,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":268,"left":22,"right":23,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":389,"left":276,"right":388,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":26,"right":275,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":27,"right":274,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":274,"left":28,"right":29,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":388,"left":286,"right":387,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":277,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":30,"right":31,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":285,"left":282,"right":284,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":282,"left":279,"right":281,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":32,"right":278,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":278,"left":33,"right":34,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":35,"right":280,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":280,"left":36,"right":37,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":283,"right":40,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":283,"left":38,"right":39,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":387,"left":314,"right":386,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":314,"left":294,"right":313,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":294,"left":289,"right":293,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":289,"left":41,"right":288,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":288,"left":42,"right":287,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":43,"right":44,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":293,"left":45,"right":292,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":292,"left":46,"right":291,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":291,"left":47,"right":290,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":290,"left":48,"right":49,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":313,"left":304,"right":312,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":304,"left":301,"right":303,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":295,"right":300,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":300,"left":52,"right":299,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":299,"left":53,"right":298,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":298,"left":54,"right":297,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":55,"right":296,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":296,"left":56,"right":57,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":58,"right":302,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":302,"left":59,"right":60,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":312,"left":308,"right":311,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":306,"right":307,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":306,"left":305,"right":63,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":305,"left":61,"right":62,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":307,"left":64,"right":65,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":311,"left":66,"rig